frames.caption: A majestic silver dragon looms over a solitary figure standing in a serene, reflective body of water. The scene is set against a backdrop of rugged, snow-dusted mountains and a cloudy sky.
frames.description: The image depicts a fantastical encounter between a large, metallic dragon and a person in a red coat. The setting is a tranquil, icy landscape with a reflective water surface, creating a mystical and awe-inspiring atmosphere.

frames.caption: A lone figure in a red coat stands on the edge of a serene body of water, facing a massive, shimmering dragon. The dragon's scales glisten in the light, reflecting the cloudy sky above. Rugged, snow-dusted cliffs frame the scene, adding to the dramatic encounter.
frames.description: The scene depicts a fantastical encounter between a human and a dragon in a remote, icy landscape. The setting is tranquil yet charged with tension, as the human stands fearlessly before the majestic creature.
